况，证明并不是自己的储存有问题。 对于自己火腿肠变质，客服提出“只赔偿1根火腿肠的钱”，这样的处理方式未获女生认同，最终，在平台客服的介入下，女生收到了整单的赔偿，也就是一箱子火腿肠的钱。 本来女生吃到变质的火腿肠，是商品质量问题导致的，如果要求店铺带自己去医院检查身体也是应该的，但女生接受了平台的协调，没有进一步作出什么要求，作为商家应该“知足”地把精力放在商品质量的把关上了，毕竟是你商品确实存在质量问题，但这样的处理方式却让客服人员气不顺了，竟然在退款后第二天“找事”了。 客服本是与顾客直接沟通，协助商品变现、解决矛盾的，但是这名“找事”的客服却缺乏专业精神，与顾客杠起来，在聊天窗口内涵起顾客的学校。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ip7yjvfbD8ZMeEAMaCDc4ODMzMjI2IPeBgpIGMGY4gBBAAXIJNTI0NDgyMjU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"1823 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e992407ea33d18c7c6e25ab2465dd2c8_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1648448055.3033924","card_id":"Q_524389446","target":{"id":524389446,"title":"乌克兰已经明确表明不加入北约，为什么俄不撤军？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/524389446","type":"question","created":1648357169,"answer_count":526,"follower_count":727,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5548,30738,136525],"comment_count":71,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ip7yjvfbD8ZMeEAMaCDc4ODEyNTI2ILHe/5EGMEc41wVAAnIJNTI0Mzg5NDQ2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"1571 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e2daa55601ac7a7c5d1a988152b201c4_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1648448055.3039842","card_id":"Q_518355959","target":{"id":518355959,"title":"大脑为啥要删除3岁前的记忆？你小时候到底看见了啥？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/518355959","type":"question","created":1645633876,"answer_count":236,"follower_count":833,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3352,4516,5633,23174,23429],"comment_count":33,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"你最早的记忆出现在什么时候，没有几个人记得吧"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ip7yjvfbD8ZMeEAMaCDc3NDcyMTAyI